OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774876271
OL,3,CMental health day centres across
OL,4,CCornwall to shut
OL,6,FCouncil-run day support for people
OL,7,Fstruggling with their mental health
OL,8,Facross Cornwall will end this week.
OL,10,FCornwall Council-owned buildings in
OL,11,FCamborne, Truro, Falmouth, Penzance,
OL,12,FSt Austell and Bude will close by
OL,13,FTuesday, 31 March, as part of "wider
OL,14,Fchanges to how support is provided
OL,15,Flocally." Mental health day centres
OL,16,Fhad previously operated at ten sites
OL,17,Facross Cornwall.
OL,26,@uD@_OUwD@IO]
