OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774876271
OL,3,CMental health day centres across
OL,4,CCornwall to shut
OL,6,FA new provider had been appointed to
OL,7,Fdeliver a redesigned service, however
OL,8,FCornwall Partnership NHS Foundation
OL,9,FTrust has been informed that it has
OL,10,Fwithdrawn.
OL,12,FThe council says everyone currently
OL,13,Fusing its services is being supported
OL,14,Fto access suitable alternatives in
OL,15,Ftheir local area from 1 April,
OL,16,Fincluding a personal review of the
OL,17,Fsupport they receive.
