OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774876271
OL,3,CMental health day centres across
OL,4,CCornwall to shut
OL,6,FCornwall Partnership NHS Foundation
OL,7,FTrust sites in Launceston and Liskeard
OL,8,Fwill continue to serve as a base for
OL,9,Fother community mental health services.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Cornwall Council
OL,12,Fsaid that while the future of trust-
OL,13,Fowned buildings in Bodmin and Newquay
OL,14,Fis yet to be determined, the trust
OL,15,Fworks closely with nearby sites that
OL,16,Fprovide mental health day activities
OL,17,Fsuch as Newquay Orchard.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
