PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774876271
OL,3,CMental health day centres across
OL,4,CCornwall to shut
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the NHS Foundation
OL,7,FTrust said: "The trust has provided
OL,8,Fmental health day resource centre
OL,9,Fservices on behalf of Cornwall Council
OL,10,Fsince the early 2000s.
OL,12,F"Following a review of those services,
OL,13,Fwe were notified that the current
OL,14,Fagreement between the trust and the
OL,15,Fcouncil will end on March 31.
OL,26,@oD@MOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
