OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774876271
OL,3,CMental health day centres across
OL,4,CCornwall to shut
OL,6,F"We were initially informed a new
OL,7,Fprovider had been appointed by the
OL,8,Fcouncil to deliver a redesigned
OL,9,Fservice from April 1. However, we have
OL,10,Fnow been informed that the provider
OL,11,Fhas withdrawn.
OL,13,F"We are writing to service users to
OL,14,Fkeep them informed and ensure they
OL,15,Fcontinue to receive support from
OL,16,Fservices the council already
OL,17,Fcommissions."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
