OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774876271
OL,3,CMental health day centres across
OL,4,CCornwall to shut
OL,6,FA representative of Cornwall Council
OL,7,Fadded: "We know some of the existing
OL,8,Fcentres are old and not the best
OL,9,Fenvironment for delivering the person-
OL,10,Fcentred, recovery-focused support,
OL,11,Fclose to home, that service users told
OL,12,Fus they value during recent engagement.
OL,14,F"This change is not about withdrawing
OL,15,Ffunding or support. The aim is to make
OL,16,Fsure people continue to receive help
OL,17,Fin ways that feel more personal,
OL,18,Fflexible and supportive of their
OL,19,Fwellbeing, as well as expanding other
OL,20,Fservices so more people can access
OL,21,Fthem.
OL,26,@oD@HOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774876271
OL,3,CMental health day centres across
OL,4,CCornwall to shut
OL,6,F"Cornwall Council and Cornwall
OL,7,FPartnership NHS Foundation Trust
OL,8,Fremain committed to delivering the
OL,9,Fbest quality and best value health
OL,10,Fservices for those who need them."
OL,12,FWe have approached Cornwall Council
OL,13,Ffor further comment on the NHS trust's
OL,14,Fstatement.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]
